<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV83">
<l>viḷarik kuralaṉṟil meṉpeṭai mēkiṉṟa muṉṟiṟpeṇṇai</l>
<l>muḷarik kurampai yituvitu vāka mukilvaṇṇaṉpēr</l>
<l>kiḷarik kiḷarip pitaṟṟummel lāviyu naivumellān</l>
<l>taḷariṟ kolōvaṟi yēṉuyya lāvatit taiyalukkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While that the nest of thorny twigs in the Palmyra tree in the frontyard</l>
<l>inhabited by the tender female of the Aṉṟil with Viḷari voice, becomes just this,</l>
<l>my tender soul too languishes, babbling out in the open the names of him with cloud colour.</l>
<l>If all will turn weak? I don’t know. Is there escaping for this woman?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
